adjectives.description: toey (comparative toeier or more toey or toeyer, superlative toeiest or most toey or toeyest)

entries.meaning: (slang, chiefly Australia) Agitated, anticipatory, excited (sometimes specifically sexually so), nervous.
examples: “You’re toeyer than a chook caught in a swag.”
She rolled her eyes. “I still don’t know what you mean.”
